\par }\pard\plain \s16\qj\nowidctlpar\adjustright \lang1031 {\lang2057 <#/>TWO Tanzanian chemists have warned that the 4.2bn/- Moshi pesticides plant being constructed by the National Chemical Industries (NCI) here will
 cause serious damage to the environment and human life. 
